NAME
  vtkSHYXShapeSmoothing
DESCRIPTION
  "Shape smoothing on triangulated vtkPolyData using CGAL PMP (smooth_shape / angle_and_area_smoothing / fair) with sharp-edge + threshold-mask vertex constraints and volume-preservation options."
GROUPS
  Meshing
DEPENDS
  vtkCGALAlgorithm
  VTK::FiltersCore
PRIVATE_DEPENDS
  VTK::CommonCore
  VTK::CommonDataModel
  VTK::CommonExecutionModel
